title: #78 - Jacksepticeye
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we're joined by YouTuber Jacksepticeye! Together we discuss therapy, Hunter x Hunter and other anime, YouTuber burnout, taxes, positive mental attitude, and of course.. wiping technique. Jacksepticeye is one of the world's biggest YouTubers who just recently hit the 20 million subscriber mark!
